{"tid":1532120,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Fact checked 真係有螢光粉","createTime":"2019-09-02T12:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T00:14:31.000Z","uid":97011,"like":265,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"4d98aa2a02331a27d06e364bfb30f619284983c1","tid":1532120,"uid":97011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eNohNbQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeNohNbQ.jpg&h=c11021ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n831去左行街 見過直昇機係頭頂 92去到1830就走<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gE2yky4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgE2yky4.jpg&h=15f1a0ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到post即刻買左支uv筆<br />\n返去照過袋 手腳 面 雨傘<br />\n咩都見唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ZiqbFT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ZiqbFT.jpg&h=7313c81b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FkGLbFY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFkGLbFY.jpg&h=afa5fe18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n解釋<br />\n1. 冇螢光粉呢單野<br />\n2. d粉咁啱冇顏射我<br />\n3. 我出街嗰段時間冇發射<br />\n4. 文具鋪uv筆冇用<br />\n5. 並非用直昇機放<br />\n6. 歡迎補充<br />\n<br />\n支持Fact check"},{"pid":"8c0efba24b4149ed60e14d5e39514c7bc49591cb","tid":1532120,"uid":315924,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:21:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫推到江永祥仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n仲有幾個鐘就返學啦好緊張<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529552\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529552</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"62bca5badf6431f79e3e1db9e982503fa5c7142d","tid":1532120,"uid":761,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:22:10.000Z","msg":"十點鳩叫行動！！！！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Av5cBad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAv5cBad.jpg&h=53535c10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p4pT43z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp4pT43z.jpg&h=df08fc7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TH9T43A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTH9T43A.jpg&h=5ee30c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04MOTWW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04MOTWW.png&h=5666d4ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eL579vg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeL579vg.jpg&h=3a5dd848&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4db1f5f2c1ee58a0c0dd8f8eb6587186b65dce5","tid":1532120,"uid":97011,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:22:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d14f2370d2f8f358e89f4887d7b5125d993cdc3","tid":1532120,"uid":97011,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:22:56.000Z","msg":"補充：<br />\n7. 可能可以用水洗甩"},{"pid":"7e863d4ca184a57226bd686ad00334f8aecf5bca","tid":1532120,"uid":97011,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:24:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c06f59cb02a23b4f2303e11051268034e35a2498","tid":1532120,"uid":97011,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:25:10.000Z","msg":"推到比人見到"},{"pid":"dc1f03880d26f3433d00b5ce0118ea5b34357f31","tid":1532120,"uid":97011,"like":0,"dislike":1,"s