動，無行動去商場涼冷氣教育自由行。<br />\n8. 每星期去連儂貼3張文宣<br />\n9. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n10. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n11. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n12. Tag或吹你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n<br />\n諗到再加，如果你咁都做唔到，講咩野好忟好惱無野可做。<br />\n只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"2bac676971901e6bb86fbfb03699a3f179c8da2d","tid":1532120,"uid":97011,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"87179bfc1db2f81bc76dfe63a1ee0a454aa713e6","tid":1532120,"uid":167548,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:29:03.000Z","msg":"你好彩先沒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:30:34.000Z","msg":"咁都可以證明唔係好大規模"},{"pid":"ab41d88d6645dc005a7e3c82b51ff98ec15e0958","tid":1532120,"uid":56700,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"87179bfc1db2f81bc76dfe63a1ee0a454aa713e6","tid":1532120,"uid":167548,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:29:03.000Z","msg":"你好彩先沒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:30:45.000Z","msg":"沒你老母"},{"pid":"921929c7a0adac691774981e52efe47e8acdf8d3","tid":1532120,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:32:15.000Z","msg":"七點先扔"},{"pid":"e809fb4e26fd220eaf0ff5958738ca8407754aed","tid":1532120,"uid":97011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:32:16.000Z","msg":"支持fact check"},{"pid":"55f0088e832ee20e2527a930d472af97ef745fed","tid":1532120,"uid":40779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:32:44.000Z","msg":"8.31"},{"pid":"92328f42433f83da203e7b3668d4db4204654a83","tid":1532120,"uid":241566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"921929c7a0adac691774981e52efe47e8acdf8d3","tid":1532120,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:32:15.000Z","msg":"七點先扔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:32:54.000Z","msg":"1831扔"},{"pid":"49e8fd3563fe450e13ade0c673d00b1cc6110b95","tid":1532120,"uid":192851,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:34:34.000Z","msg":"其實我都唔太相信係用直升機，始終現場風大，咁幼既粉喺10樓